{"tid":1662041,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony Xperia 5 電池續航測試，結果竟超越 iPhone 11 Pro！","createTime":"2019-10-18T13:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T09:05:30.000Z","uid":1886,"like":20,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a77d1ac587d02b5de272c248ca2305de5e505f5b","tid":1662041,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T13:38:05.000Z","msg":"Xperia 5 是 Sony 於上月初在 IFA 2019 上推出的一款 &ldquo;細芒&rdquo; 電話，雖然尺寸達到了 6.1吋，但是 21:9 的比例使得這款電話的寬度並不大，差不多就是 4.7 吋的 iPhone 7 的寬度，也就是單手可以輕鬆握持。但是，想單手玩這款電話&hellip;？除非你的大拇指夠長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.xfastest.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/sony-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2Fsony-3.jpg&h=cee1733e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在相對小巧的機身內部， Sony 為這款電話配備了一顆 3140mAh 容量電池，支援 PD 快叉。對於這塊電池的續航能力，外媒 PhoneArena 對不同使用場景進行了測試，並且得出結論：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.xfastest.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/sony-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2Fsony-3.jpg&h=cee1733e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在遊戲測試部分，Xperia 5 竟能夠連續支援5小時58分的遊戲時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />；三星 S10e 4小時19分、iPhone 11 Pro 3小時48分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、三星S10 3小時42分、iPhone 11 3小時39分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/sony/71075/phonearena-said-that-sony-xperia-5-is-really-good-for-gaming/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fsony%2F71075%2Fphonearena-said-that-sony-xperia-5-is-really-good-for-gaming%2F&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9ssFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=8ba1b044\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/sony/71075/phonearena-said-that-sony-xperia-5-is-really-good-for-gaming/</a>"},{"pid":"06485bf6e58c7a8b69aa98c315600c5e66e52211","tid":1662041,"uid":12628,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:12:32.000Z","msg":"成篇文章咁多，做咩講啲唔講啲咁避重就輕呀，<br />\n幫你貼晒佢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ho1xPdv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fho1xPdv.jpg&h=da702d86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb73468f83d60c99930e26307a528d5c95528372","tid":1662041,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"06485bf6e58c7a8b69aa98c315600c5e66e52211","tid":1662041,"uid":12628,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:12:32.000Z","msg":"成篇文章咁多，做咩講啲唔講啲咁避重就輕呀，<br />\n幫你貼晒佢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ho1xPdv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fho1xPdv.jpg&h=da702d86&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:54:46.000Z","msg":"咁快彈出嚟做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39cd91dff5c385428cc84909cac6ed956ba0c093","tid":1662041,"uid":89514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:06:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f28e5c3dd96e2676ef73dcef6eddc79fa2852bf2","tid":1662041,"uid":145277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:08:28.000Z","msg":"Sony 啲 code name亂到"},{"pid":"4c9e29d3e1d2c9e04068d9183202598894b65672","tid":1662041,"uid":145277,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:10:19.000Z","msg":"s10e嘅電力表現最出色"},{"pid":"6a150f3188dd4437caed307afbed790493fa1699","tid":1662041,"uid":63154,"like":11,"dislike":7,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T15:21:49.000Z","msg":"sony軟件係咁多個大牌子最差"},{"pid":"f63678084416d05e0d8e3739b91f09b4bf2d83a6","tid":1662041,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":12,"scor